   FILES

     XPSLIBDIRX/*.afm      AFM (Adobe Font Metrics) files for use with
                           enscript(1).  The names of these AFM files as
                           shipped with the TRANSCRIPT release are abbrevi-
                           ated, and the resource file afmfiles.upr provides
                           the mapping between font name and AFM file name.

     XDITDIRX              Directory containing font families for
                           [di]troff(1)

     XTROFFFONTDIRX        Directory containing font families for [o]troff(1)

